{"tid":1210560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"防火小知識","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:06:39.000Z","uid":256835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75afe7bc4e1eae604ddd45bc25c25c848df85be1","tid":1210560,"uid":256835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8Gb2VF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8Gb2VF.png&h=7843e655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察好似好燥底咁<br />\n擔心佢地會著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教教大家正確選擇滅火器具:<br />\n<br />\n1. 二氧化碳氣體式滅火筒<br />\n適用於:<br />\n電火、燃燒中之任何易燃液體、 電子儀器或文件等。<br />\n注意:<br />\n二氧化碳可以令人窒息，使用 滅火筒後，應走往空曠地方。<br />\n<br />\n2. 乾粉式滅火筒<br />\n適用於:<br />\n大多數火警，包括電火或 燃燒中之易燃液體。<br />\n注意:<br />\n噴出的乾粉會減低能見度，令人難以 辨別方向。"},{"pid":"06cd64d1b5713fb38619b8101ed0df12814e99b6","tid":1210560,"uid":256835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75afe7bc4e1eae604ddd45bc25c25c848df85be1","tid":1210560,"uid":256835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8Gb2VF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8Gb2VF.png&h=7843e655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察好似好燥底咁<br />\n擔心佢地會著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教教大家正確選擇滅火器具:<br />\n<br />\n1. 二氧化碳氣體式滅火筒<br />\n適用於:<br />\n電火、燃燒中之任何易燃液體、 電子儀器或文件等。<br />\n注意:<br />\n二氧化碳可以令人窒息，使用 滅火筒後，應走往空曠地方。<br />\n<br />\n2. 乾粉式滅火筒<br />\n適用於:<br />\n大多數火警，包括電火或 燃燒中之易燃液體。<br />\n注意:<br />\n噴出的乾粉會減低能見度，令人難以 辨別方向。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}